Meteara stands back and sits. Her large tail curls up around her.

Meteara: Why do you keep comparing me with the first emissary? Your 
internal battles mean nothing to me, whereas it was precisely where 
the first emissary intervened. I am as likely to kill you as I would 
your enemy. Stop bothering, nothing except a direct hit will make me 
move to fight now.
